{"tid":2098003,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中大生甩襲警罪：影片證據重要","createTime":"2020-07-07T07:35:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T09:08:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4d6946f0d5c8b6c38113d5114a1843ac88ce18e4","tid":2098003,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:35:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200707/KABYXONVIC36ZSQHXPSN5RLK3Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200707%2FKABYXONVIC36ZSQHXPSN5RLK3Q%2F&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivd8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=4c2e0a1f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200707%2FKABYXONVIC36ZSQHXPSN5RLK3Q%2F&h=fd8a4765\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200707/KABYXONVIC36ZSQHXPSN5RLK3Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中大生甩襲警罪：影片證據重要<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1x0b-2fmmy99u8MneIZ0C1HowWs=/640x424/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3L5XPYLYYO2MRZ5W36TSTA3DCE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1x0b-2fmmy99u8MneIZ0C1HowWs%3D%2F640x424%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3L5XPYLYYO2MRZ5W36TSTA3DCE.jpg&h=23a6d05f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員陳勁翔<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年8月25日的荃葵青遊行演變成警民衝突，<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n呼籲市民「睇睇自己手機」，如錄下有用片段可聯絡信任的人。<br />\n<br />\n21歲被告祝嘉樂脫罪後稱：「好感恩呢段時間幫我好多嘅人，我知道呢段時間很難捱，希望有案在身嘅朋友多啲休息。」他另呼籲市民若發現手機有有用的片，可聯絡信任的人如律師。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官指警「撠」「推」混淆<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：逼網絡商提供用戶身份<br />\n<br />\n被告被控去年8月25日在荃灣街市街與眾安街交界的香港電訊1010店外襲擊警員陳勁翔。<br />\n<br />\n劉官裁決時指片段顯示被告的手觸碰陳的盾牌時仍高舉電話拍攝；而陳亦指看不到被告襲擊，只感到被告向他施壓。劉官指如被告用力施壓，手應向前伸並有距離才可發力，但片段中看不到，只見他身貼盾牌。<br />\n<br />\n另外，陳跌倒當刻稱「你撠我」，劉官指如陳感被絆倒，應是下肢以下被觸碰，與用手推不同，明顯涉及兩個部位、並有一定距離，亦是兩個截然不同的動作，不會混淆，故對陳的證供存疑；基於疑點利益歸於被告，裁定被告脫罪。<br />\n<br />\n警員陳勁翔早前供稱案發時被告拍攝被截查女子，<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n偵緝警長郭俊祺當時聲稱：「𠵱家話你非法集結，唔係話你襲警呀！」<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC3484/19"},{"pid":"9a6aa18cbddc37be32d1fff9948c74f257d79388","tid":2098003,"uid":9116,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:36:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EnWzf2M.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEnWzf2M.gif&h=37ab8849&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d94e7c367f812b4d99078d08c952495631e2b297","tid":2098003,"uid":249885,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:37:13.000Z","msg":"一時又唔俾影 一時又要片做證據😅"},{"pid":"50b5afe300c8d5118a6bd546cb6e87892c1097ee","tid":2098003,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:37:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>近日新增大量本地確診</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家出街一定要戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n勤力洗手<br />\n<br />\n唔好去人多既地方</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">希望政府可以立即停課，收緊限聚令，停gym房，戲院，k房等</span></span>"},{"pid":"51fea54f9f3e9df8129150fccdc6338834c4aa6b","tid":2098003,"uid":246884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:38:25.000Z","msg":"手足一世平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b562b0b5bd8f008e8af16426e905a88d93ab5e2","tid":2098003,"uid":345459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:39:20.000Z","msg":"黑警仍是是可靠證人？<br />\n不是"},{"pid":"4c44d38d01bf082a44f55a200cdcd514fb92ad3b","tid":2098003,"uid":76365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51fea54f9f3e9df8129150fccdc6338834c4aa6b","tid":2098003,"uid":246884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:38:25.000Z","msg":"手足一世平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src